        "text": "οἱ γνωστοὶ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", His acquaintances, Galileans mostly, who stood till the end, but far away. Mt. and Mk. do not mention this. No word of the eleven.—",
        "children": []
