        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "καὶ γυναῖκες",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ": warm-hearted Galileans they too, and ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "women",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", therefore bolder where the heart was concerned; nearer presumably, therefore “seeing” predicted of them specially (",
        "children": []
